    <div class="repair-category">
      <h3>iPhone Screen Repair & Replacement</h3>
      <p>A cracked or shattered iPhone screen is one of the most common issues we repair. Our screen replacement service restores your iPhone to perfect working condition using premium-quality LCD and OLED displays that match original specifications.</p>
      <p><strong>Common screen issues we fix:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Cracked or shattered glass from drops and impacts</li>
        <li>Non-responsive or malfunctioning touchscreen (ghost touches, dead zones)</li>
        <li>LCD damage causing display lines, black spots, or discolouration</li>
        <li>Broken Face ID or front camera assembly</li>
        <li>Screen separation or lifting from the frame</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We stock genuine-quality replacement screens for all iPhone models and can typically complete screen repairs in under an hour. All screen replacements include thorough testing of touch responsiveness, Face ID functionality, and True Tone display calibration where applicable.</p>
      <a href="{{ section.settings.screen_repair_url | default: '/collections/iphone-screen-repair' }}" class="repair-link">View Screen Repair Pricing →</a>
    </div>

    <!-- iPhone Battery Replacement -->
    <div class="repair-category">
      <h3>iPhone Battery Replacement</h3>
      <p>Is your iPhone battery draining quickly, shutting down unexpectedly, or not holding a charge? We offer professional battery replacement services using high-capacity batteries that meet or exceed original specifications.</p>
      <p><strong>Signs you need a battery replacement:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Battery drains faster than 20% per hour with normal use</li>
        <li>iPhone shuts down unexpectedly, especially below 30% charge</li>
        <li>Battery Health showing below 80% capacity in Settings</li>
        <li>Phone only works when connected to charger</li>
        <li>Swollen or expanded battery causing screen lifting</li>
        <li>Overheating during charging or regular use</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Our battery replacement service includes proper disposal of your old battery, installation of a certified replacement, and full diagnostics to ensure optimal performance. Most battery replacements are completed within 30-45 minutes.</p>
      <a href="{{ section.settings.battery_repair_url | default: '/collections/iphone-battery-replacement' }}" class="repair-link">View Battery Replacement Pricing →</a>
