    <!-- iPhone Charging Port Repair -->
    <div class="repair-category">
      <h3>iPhone Charging Port Repair</h3>
      <p>Charging port issues can prevent your iPhone from charging properly or connecting to accessories. We repair or replace faulty charging ports, restoring full functionality to your device.</p>
      <p><strong>Charging port problems we resolve:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>iPhone not charging or only charging at certain angles</li>
        <li>Loose or wobbly charging cable connection</li>
        <li>Lint, debris, or corrosion inside the charging port</li>
        <li>Bent or broken charging port pins</li>
        <li>Water damage affecting charging functionality</li>
        <li>CarPlay or data transfer not working via cable</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We start with a thorough cleaning and inspection of your charging port. If replacement is necessary, we use high-quality charging port assemblies and test all functions including charging speed, data transfer, and audio output to ensure everything works perfectly.</p>
      <a href="{{ section.settings.charging_port_url | default: '/collections/iphone-charging-port-repair' }}" class="repair-link">View Charging Port Repair Pricing →</a>
