      <p>Damaged housing or rear glass does not just affect your iPhone's appearance-it can compromise structural integrity and water resistance. We offer professional housing and back glass replacement services.</p>
      <p><strong>Housing and rear glass repairs include:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Cracked or shattered rear glass panel replacement</li>
        <li>Bent or damaged chassis straightening or replacement</li>
        <li>Camera lens glass replacement</li>
