      <h3>How long does an iPhone repair take?</h3>
      <p>Most common iPhone repairs, such as screen replacements and battery changes, are completed within 30 minutes to 1 hour while you wait. More complex repairs like charging port replacements or water damage restoration may take 2-4 hours. We always provide an estimated completion time when you book your repair, and we will notify you immediately if we discover any additional issues that might extend the repair time.</p>
