    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Do you offer same-day iPhone repair services?</h3>
      <p>Yes! We offer same-day repair services for most iPhone issues at our repair centres. For screen repairs, battery replacements, and charging port fixes, we typically complete repairs the same day you bring your device in-often within an hour. For more complex repairs or mail-in services, we aim to complete and return your iPhone within 24 to 48 hours. Contact us to check availability for your specific repair and location.</p>
