      <p>While walk-ins are welcome at all our locations, we recommend booking an appointment to ensure minimal waiting time and guaranteed same-day service. Booking ahead allows us to allocate a technician and reserve the necessary parts for your specific iPhone model. You can book online through our website, call us directly, or use our live chat. For urgent repairs, contact us and we will do our best to accommodate you as quickly as possible, even without an appointment.</p>
